{"tid":1232920,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(戰術討論) (再開) 有無人可以重整到612嘅時間線","createTime":"2019-06-16T16:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T02:36:22.000Z","uid":37673,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9522eb8883e85583f131a5aac90b3e3216fb3f36","tid":1232920,"uid":37673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"睇完中信個post <br />\n相信大家612都發過一場大夢 但好多人都唔清楚其他戰線發先過咩事 <br />\n而每個地方都有其戰略價值 大家可以整合返D狗既進攻模式會對將來既夢境有所幫助<br />\n希望大家一直修正 <br />\n<br />\n我先講 <br />\n08:00 夏慤道龍和道成功出到去<br />\n<br />\n11:00 龍和道灣仔方向防線推前至龍合街<br />\n15:00 龍景街開始多狗<br />\n15:10 煲底攻入<br />\n15:50 狗出槍同催淚彈<br />\n16:10 龍合街狗直接黑催淚龍合街防線<br />\n16:15 狗進攻至立法會道同添美道並攻擊大台 另外利用夏慤道封死添美道 只可向中信逃走<br />\n16:15 龍和道灣仔方向防線完全失守 向中環碼頭逃走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6f766398a263f19dd644b134c831213e93c98b","tid":1232920,"uid":37673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f79a95bf99fcb7d93f992b63870ae7569dbfaf1","tid":1232920,"uid":42215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:11:52.000Z","msg":"我個夢係1520啲狗退入煲底引人入去<br />\n1530-1540開始放彈，之後同你差不多"},{"pid":"0417af6cdf68cca7872467f7041803e092286a06","tid":1232920,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ba9ff414cbd218367222066e33741003c621b3","tid":1232920,"uid":37673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f79a95bf99fcb7d93f992b63870ae7569dbfaf1","tid":123